8 hours and 12 minutes, she's sleeping well

13
00:08:48,800 --> 00:08:51,730
The legendary soldier is so cute when she's sleeping

14
00:08:54,900 --> 00:08:56,560
About your body, will you...?

15
00:09:01,200 --> 00:09:02,670
She will be surprised

16
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:05,860
when we get to Utopia

17
00:09:07,200 --> 00:09:08,630
Utopia, huh...

18
00:09:09,800 --> 00:09:13,350
Olympus A5, do we have permission to land?

19
00:09:15,400 --> 00:09:18,210
Don't get too close before ID is confirmed

20
00:09:18,411 --> 00:09:21,020
or the Fortress cannon will fire

21
00:09:21,500 --> 00:09:23,290
Olympus A5, come in

22
